  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to compare the efficacy of intercalating chemotherapy (gefitinib and
      pemetrexed/cisplatin) and chemotherapy (navelbine/cisplatin) in completely resected NSCLC
      with common EGFR mutations.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
